      • uiReadyCitation

        public static CitationBuilder uiReadyCitation()
        Creates a new, ui ready, CitationBuilder with the following fields set
        • Incident - a new ui ready injury incident
        • CitationAuthority - set to a unique code of the form AuthorityN
        • CitationCode - set to a unique code of the form CodeN
        • CitationNumber - set to a unique number of the form 123N
        • CitationType - a randomly selected citation type
          Returns:
          a new ui ready builder
